<post_id>310015471669190</post_id>

The Facebook post promotes a two-day intensive training course organized by AGXecutive, focusing on agribusiness. The content is entirely unrelated to the parliamentary elections.  There is no mention of any political candidate, party, or any attempt to influence voters. The post's objective is purely promotional, aiming to attract participants to the training event.  The paid advertisement targets a broad audience interested in professional development within the agribusiness sector.  Therefore, it does not meet the criteria for electoral propaganda as defined by Article 36 (7) of LEGE nr. 334 din 17 iulie 2006 and Article 98 t) of LEGE nr. 208 din 20 iulie 2015.
